# Stable GRU-based Hammerstein benchmark runner
#
# Core design preserved from attached V6 family:
# - GRU-only nonlinear block
# - latent_dim = 2
# - full-sequence training
# - Stage-1 step-signal initialization
# - Stage-2 random-signal training
#
# Strong synthetic benchmark mode:
# - deterministic target = X (noise-free simulator output)
# - measured-output tracking still evaluated on Y
# - noise head still trained on residuals to Y
#
# New in this script:
# - Run multiple seeds automatically
# - Save per-seed metrics/results
# - Aggregate mean ± std across seeds
# ============================================================

